            "11": "<font class=\"jw\">Blessed are ye, when\n   <i>men</i> shall revile you, and persecute <i>you</i>, and\n   shall say all manner of evil against you falsely, for my\n   sake.</font>",
            "12": "<font class=\"jw\">Rejoice, and be exceeding\n   glad: for great <i>is</i> your reward in heaven: for so\n   persecuted they the prophets which were before you.</font>",
