            "30": "<font class=\"jw\">And if thy right hand offend\n   thee, cut it off, and cast <i>it</i> from thee: for it is\n   profitable for thee that one of thy members should perish, and\n   not <i>that</i> thy whole body should be cast into\n   hell.</font>",
            "31": "<font class=\"jw\">It hath been said, Whosoever\n   shall put away his wife, let him give her a writing of\n   divorcement:</font>",
