            "33": "<font class=\"jw\">Again, ye have heard that it\n   hath been said by them of old time, Thou shalt not forswear\n   thyself, but shalt perform unto the Lord thine\n   oaths:</font>",
            "34": "<font class=\"jw\">But I say unto you, Swear not\n   at all; neither by heaven; for it is God's throne:</font>",
