            "36": "<font class=\"jw\">Neither shalt thou swear by\n   thy head, because thou canst not make one hair white or\n   black.</font>",
            "37": "<font class=\"jw\">But let your communication\n   be, Yea, yea; Nay, nay: for whatsoever is more than these\n   cometh of evil.</font>",
            "38": "<font class=\"jw\">Ye have heard that it hath\n   been said, An eye for an eye, and a tooth for a\n   tooth:</font>",
            "39": "<font class=\"jw\">But I say unto you, That ye\n   resist not evil: but whosoever shall smite thee on thy right\n   cheek, turn to him the other also.</font>",
            "40": "<font class=\"jw\">And if any man will sue thee\n   at the law, and take away thy coat, let him have <i>thy</i>\n   cloak also.</font>",
